{"tid":812304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵考慮制裁以網絡攻擊偷美國智識產權既公司 Mnuchin反對","createTime":"2018-09-09T13:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T14:04:37.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77dc0057899df4ff564f4774bfa35be02abd20e6","tid":812304,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:52:38.000Z","msg":"The Trump administration is considering imposing sanctions on Chinese entities caught stealing U.S. intellectual property via cyber attacks, three people familiar with the matter said.<br />\n<br />\nThe plan being discussed would use an Obama administration executive order that allows the U.S. to impose sanctions on individuals or entities engaging in &ldquo;malicious cyber-enabled activities.&rdquo; But it has sparked a heated debate among administration officials, with Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin, who has jurisdiction over the potential sanctions, said to be blocking the effort, the people said.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-09-07/trump-advisers-said-to-weigh-hacking-sanctions-on-china-in-trade\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2018-09-07%2Ftrump-advisers-said-to-weigh-hacking-sanctions-on-china-in-trade&d=QCTgwV6Mof7IJ8TWPZeZdV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b1eedd8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-09-07/trump-advisers-said-to-weigh-hacking-sanctions-on-china-in-trade</a>"},{"pid":"755083782eaff90f5826b3d464229aa2522ae345","tid":812304,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"知識產權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542843f7cb8dbfe18deec1d30b366cc64e57dd0c","tid":812304,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/